-- Create BikeStation table with matching data types (internal sql table)

CREATE TABLE BikeStation (
    Number NVARCHAR(100), 
    Name NVARCHAR(100),
    Latitude FLOAT,
    Longitude FLOAT,
    District NVARCHAR(100),
    Is_Public NVARCHAR(100),
    docks INT
);
GO

-- Insert data into AggBlueBike
INSERT INTO AggBlueBike (
    Number, 
    Name,
    Latitude,
    Longitude,
    District,
    Is_Public,
    docks
)
SELECT
    Number, 
    Name,
    Latitude,
    Longitude,
    District,
    Is_Public,
    docks
FROM 
    ExternalBikeStation;
GO
